### 3. Token Validation Flow — `GET /api/auth/validate?token=...`

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant AC as AuthController
    participant AS as AuthService
    participant JS as JwtService

    C->>AC: GET /api/auth/validate?token=xxx
    AC->>AS: validateToken(token)
    AS->>JS: validateToken(token)
    JS->>JS: Parse JWT, check expiration
    JS-->>AS: true / false
    AS-->>AC: boolean
    AC-->>C: 200 OK {"valid": true/false}
```

> [!NOTE]
> This endpoint is used by **other microservices** to verify tokens issued by the auth service.

