### 4. Authenticated Request Flow (Protected Endpoints)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant SF as SecurityFilterChain
    participant JF as JwtAuthenticationFilter
    participant JS as JwtService
    participant CUDS as CustomUserDetailsService
    participant R as AuthUserRepository
    participant SC as SecurityContext
    participant EP as Protected Endpoint

    C->>SF: GET /api/some-protected-resource<br/>Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
    SF->>JF: Enter JWT filter
    JF->>JF: Extract token from header
    JF->>JS: extractEmail(token)
    JS-->>JF: user email
    JF->>CUDS: loadUserByUsername(email)
    CUDS->>R: findByEmail(email)
    R-->>CUDS: AuthUser
    CUDS-->>JF: UserDetails

    JF->>JS: validateToken(token)
    JS-->>JF: true

    JF->>SC: Set Authentication
    JF->>EP: Continue filter chain
    EP-->>C: 200 OK + Response

    alt Token Expired
        JS-->>JF: throw ExpiredJwtException
        JF-->>C: 401 "JWT token has expired"
    end

    alt Invalid Signature
        JS-->>JF: throw SignatureException
        JF-->>C: 401 "Invalid JWT signature"
    end
```

