## Security Configuration

| Rule | Configuration |
|------|---------------|
| CSRF | Disabled (intended, but **bug**: missing `@Bean`) |
| CORS | Disabled in Security + separate `CorsConfig` bean |
| Session | Stateless (`STATELESS`) |
| Public paths | `/api/auth/**`, `/error` |
| All other paths | Require authentication |
| Auth method | JWT via `JwtAuthenticationFilter` |
| Password encoding | BCrypt |

