## Inter-Service Communication

```mermaid
graph LR
    AS["Auth Service :8083"] -->|"POST /users/internal<br/>CreateUserProfileRequest"| US["User Service :8082"]
    US -->|"UserResponse"| AS
```

During **registration only**, the auth service calls the User Service via `RestTemplate` to create a user profile. This is a synchronous, blocking HTTP call.

