## Database Schema

**Table**: `auth_users`

| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `id` | UUID | PK |
| `email` | VARCHAR | UNIQUE, NOT NULL |
| `password` | VARCHAR | NOT NULL (BCrypt hash) |
| `role` | VARCHAR | NOT NULL (ENUM: `ROLE_USER`, `ROLE_MANAGER`, `ROLE_ADMIN`) |
| `created_at` | TIMESTAMP | NOT NULL |
| `updated_at` | TIMESTAMP | |
| `last_login` | TIMESTAMP | |
| `is_active` | BOOLEAN | |

Database: **PostgreSQL** on port `5433`, database name `FlowSync-AuthService`.
